
\begin{gather}
\bm{W} \leftarrow \bm{W} + \epsilon (\bm{h}^{(1)}\bm{v}^{T}- P(\bm{h}^{(k+1)}=1|\bm{v}^{(k+1)})\bm{v}^{(k+1)T}) \\
\bm{b} \leftarrow \bm{b} + \epsilon(\bm{v}-\bm{v}^{(k+1)}) \\
\bm{c} \leftarrow \bm{c} + \epsilon(\bm{h}^{(1)}-P(\bm{h}^{(k+1)}=1|\bm{v}^{(k+1)}))
\end{gather}
ただし，$\epsilon$は学習率である
